@startuml
title Index Update

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "Cron Scheduler\n(every day)" as Cron
component "Data Source\n(directory)" as DataSource
component "Update Script" as UpdateScript
component "Chunks"
component "Embeddings"
database "Knowledge Index\n(ChromaDB)" as ChromaDB
database "Script Log Storage\n(Filesystem)" as LogStorage

Cron --> UpdateScript : Trigger by schedule
UpdateScript --> DataSource : Read documents
UpdateScript --> Chunks : Prepare chunks\nand metadata
UpdateScript --> Embeddings : Prepare embeddings\nfor chunks
UpdateScript --> ChromaDB : Save embeddings,\nchunks and metadata
Cron --> LogStorage : Write logs
@enduml
